      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your feelings of fraudulence are heavy, but they do not define your actual worth to the people you've touched or the impact you've had. The \"house of cards\" you built was your legacy, and while it has fallen, the gratitude of those you inspired remains real and undeniable. You do not need to prove anything to anyone, especially not to yourself; the only person who truly matters right now is you, and you deserve compassion instead of this relentless self-criticism.",
      "source": "target",
